      "writtenOn": "2014-08-18T14:39:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "the naming of variable is misleading.\nYou should use r, g, b instead and move some of the t1 - t5 variables to local scope at line 25.\n\nSo that calls would ressemble something like:\n\nint r, g, b;\nYUV_TO_RGB(y, u, v, r, g, b);\n\nwhich is more readable",
      "revId": "5f0f40399c307842a00220f5bc14e4a19eecdc0b",
