        "id": 1004029
      },
      "writtenOn": "2014-08-18T14:51:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "if I move t1..t5 to local scope then I can not use do {} while (0) for macro. should I move them to local scope and remove do while from macro?",
      "parentUuid": "AAAAdn//bVQ\u003d",
      "revId": "5f0f40399c307842a00220f5bc14e4a19eecdc0b",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
